ZH: 我每周都要写周报。
EN: I have to write a weekly report every week.

ZH: 请将你的周报提交给我。
EN: Please submit your weekly report to me.

ZH: 这周的周报内容很详细。
EN: The content of this week's report is very detailed.

ZH: 我们需要在周报中列出下一周的计划。
EN: We need to list the next week's plan in the report.

ZH: 这份周报是根据我们的工作计划来编写的。
EN: This report is based on our work plan.

ZH: 上周的周报中有一个重要的错误。
EN: There was a major error in last week's report.

ZH: 我需要准备下周的周报模板。
EN: I need to prepare the template for next week's report.

ZH: 周报的截止日期是每周五下午五点。
EN: The deadline for the report is Friday at 5 pm.

ZH: 这份周报需要包含我们的销售数据。
EN: This report should include our sales data.

ZH: 请将本周的周报发送给所有团队成员。
EN: Please send this week's report to all team members.

ZH: 这份周报需要重点关注项目进展情况。
EN: This report needs to focus on the progress of the project.

ZH: 我在周报中提到了一些潜在的问题。
EN: I mentioned some potential issues in the report.

ZH: 周报中的总结部分需要简洁明了。
EN: The summary section of the report should be concise and clear.

ZH: 请在周报中详细描述下一周的工作安排。
EN: Please provide a detailed description of the work plan for the next week in the report.

ZH: 对于每个工作小组，周报是必须提交的。
EN: The report is mandatory for each work group.

ZH: 我们需要在周报中列出项目的里程碑。
EN: We need to list the milestones of the project in the report.

ZH: 周报中需要包含关于市场调研的结果。
EN: The report needs to include the results of the market research.

ZH: 这份周报是每周例会的一部分。
EN: This report is a part of the weekly meeting.

ZH: 周报中的图表可以更好地展示数据。
EN: Charts in the report can present the data more effectively.

ZH: 我们的周报需要每周定期更新。
EN: Our report needs to be updated regularly every week.
